# PLACEHOLDER: This file must be replaced with the actual enterprise root CA certificate.
#
# Run scripts/bootstrap-pki.sh to generate the PKI material, then copy the root CA cert:
#   cp .pki/root_ca.crt ansible/roles/workstation/files/demo-corp-root-ca.crt
#
# Do NOT commit the actual certificate if it contains sensitive organizational information.
# The root CA certificate itself is public (it only contains the public key), but
# verify your .gitignore excludes *.pem and *.crt if desired.
#
# Expected format:
# -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
# <base64-encoded DER data>
# -----END CERTIFICATE-----
